{"tid":1666053,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]點解我地會覺得鏡係銀色","createTime":"2019-10-20T22:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T12:48:44.000Z","uid":62259,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5c4a2c3e5989067a3eda56cc056cafb171f841","tid":1666053,"uid":62259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T22:11:13.000Z","msg":"鏡入面既影像都係跟現實世界顏色<br />\n如果鏡係銀色的話 咁白色物體既鏡像應該都會偏銀色<br />\n<br />\n到底鏡係咩色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5657adfa18bd9878ee717e5de0f20ed7453079f7","tid":1666053,"uid":201170,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T22:12:14.000Z","msg":"銀色 <br />\n此po已完"},{"pid":"3b1c68f32a5d45b72a8bd0ac3a3d54de40a81bbf","tid":1666053,"uid":199559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T22:12:47.000Z","msg":"鏡真係銀色 因為個底係銀色<br />\n白色鏡咪白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb00443f9b3b80ff0daabcfa06e748b65518e40","tid":1666053,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T22:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29eb2a5c6a3b08ecd9ac7bb2db7703255e73eb35","tid":1666053,"uid":103586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:59:50.000Z","msg":"我諗銀色(同金色) 呢個term<br />\n只係泛指金屬表面嗰種視覺效果<br />\n唔係真係一種顏色<br />\n<br />\n即係 譬如叫你畫塊鏡出嚟 可能你會油灰色<br />\n但你一日唔鍍層金屬落去<br />\n一日都唔會真係做到所謂銀色出嚟"},{"pid":"bc4d037b4ffbe0d0858f4a8db6ac32f90e79c41a","tid":1666053,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"鏡係綠色的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mentalfloss.com/article/67608/color-mirror-not-what-youd-expect\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmentalfloss.com%2Farticle%2F67608%2Fcolor-mirror-not-what-youd-expect&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=7ee29dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mentalfloss.com/article/67608/color-mirror-not-what-youd-expect</a>"},{"pid":"34265e1a5406ec791af6a8f6764332aa3e81547e","tid":1666053,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:48:44.000Z","msg":"鏡是鏡色的"}]}